Usage: set_default_view [-help] { [-hold <newDefaultHoldView>] [-setup <newDefaultSetupView>] }

-help                          # Prints out the command usage
-hold <newDefaultHoldView>     # Changes the default active hold analysis view
                               # to the specified analysis view (string, optional)
-setup <newDefaultSetupView>   # Changes the default setup analysis view to the
                               # specified analysis view (string, optional)